    <chapter line="1">7. Samasīsakathā</chapter>
    <subhead line="2">Samasīsakathāvaṇṇanā</subhead>
    <paragraph line="3" number="33"> Idāni <pageBreak edition="V" number="2.0287" /><pageBreak edition="P" number="3.0695" /> pāṭihāriyakathānantaraṃ ādipāṭihāriyabhūtassa iddhipāṭihāriyasaṅgahitassa samasīsibhāvassa iddhipāṭihāriyabhāvadīpanatthaṃ ñāṇakathāya niddiṭṭhāpi samasīsakathā iddhipāṭihāriyasambandhena puna kathitā. Tassā atthavaṇṇanā tattha kathitāyevāti.</paragraph>
    <centered line="4">Samasīsakathāvaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā.</centered>
